# Interview Helper is distributed as a closed-source binary.
# This public repo must never contain source code, build artifacts, secrets,
# or personal interview data. The patterns below guard against accidents.

# Source code (kept private)
src/
*.cs
*.csproj
*.xaml
*.sln

# Build artifacts and release payloads (released via GitHub Releases, never committed)
bin/
obj/
build/
dist/
dist.zip
publish/
*.zip
*.dll
*.exe
*.pdb
*.deps.json
*.runtimeconfig.json

# Secrets and keys
.env
*.env
*.key
*.pfx
*secret*
*apikey*

# Personal interview data, logs, transcripts, story logs
interviews/
logs/
*.log
*transcript*
*story-log*
*talking-point*

# Engineering docs (kept private)
BUILD_SPEC.md
*REQUIREMENTS*
*SPECIFICATION*
IMPLEMENTATION_PLAN.md
*HANDOFF*
SUPERPROMPT.md

# OS / editor noise
.vs/
*.user
*.suo
Thumbs.db
.DS_Store
